@startuml
' README / marketplace: source for media/readme-preview.png — regenerate with PlantUML CLI or Docker.
' Módulos: examples/architecture-overview.puml + architecture*.puml; docs/architecture-diagrams.md.

title PlantUML Viewer — visual pipeline (sample)

skinparam defaultFontName Verdana

actor User
participant "Custom editor" as Editor
participant "Preview webview" as Preview
participant "PlantUML server" as Server
participant "Export file" as Export

User -> Editor: edit .puml source
activate Editor
Editor -> Preview: document text
activate Preview
Preview -> Server: encode + POST
activate Server
Server --> Preview: SVG
deactivate Server
Preview --> User: pan and zoom
deactivate Preview
deactivate Editor

== Export ==
User -> Preview: export PNG or SVG
activate Preview
Preview -> Server: same diagram text
activate Server
Server --> Preview: image bytes
deactivate Server
Preview -> Export: write file
activate Export
Export --> User: saved
deactivate Export
deactivate Preview

note right of Preview
  **plantumlViewer** settings
  choose server URL and visual theme
end note

@enduml
